what_worked: Applied decorrelate, date_cte_isolate, dimension_cte_isolate, prefetch_fact_join achieving 1.13x speedup
why_it_worked: Correlated subqueries re-execute per outer row; converting to JOIN eliminates per-row overhead; Pre-filtering date dimension into CTE reduces hash join probe table from 73K to ~365 rows; Pre-filtering all dimension tables into CTEs avoids repeated full-table scans; Pre-joining filtered dimensions with fact table before aggregation reduces join input
